	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What I like about the drac battle you can play it safe or take a chance.  It's really easy to just walk away from him and make the pillars spread out, then you can walk towards him and try to get some more hits in just before the big flame sprouts.  And the cross makes it even faster.

		

